title: conferred on me by section 69(2) of the Finance Act 2024 (No. 43 of 2024),
heading: 2. The 1st day of March 2025 is appointed as the day on which section 69(1)
text_raw:
2. The 1st day of March 2025 is appointed as the day on which section 69(1) 

of the Finance Act 2024 (No. 43 of 2024) shall come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

20 February, 2025. 

PASCHAL DONOHOE, 
Minister for Finance. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 25th February, 2025.
